# ControlPanel - User

This section is a API allowing users to view users and create,delete and update them.

## Users API Root [/admin/user]

+ Headers 
    All routes has Authorization token in request.

## List All Users [GET /filter/:filter] 
+ Parameter
    + filter: {
        name: string - Name of user
        role: string - Role of user
    }
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    [
        {
            _id: string - Id of user
            createdAt: timestamp - Date of creation of user
            name: string - Name of user
            email: string - Email of user
            password: string - Password of user
            role: string - Role of user
        }
    ]

## Count Users [GET /totUsers]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    {
        count: number - Total of user
    }

## Last Inserts [GET]

return limit 5

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    [
        {
            _id: string - Id of user
            createdAt: timestamp - Date of creation of user
            name: string - Name of user
            email: string - Email of user
            password: string - Password of user
            role: string - Role of user
        }
    ]

## Find user by id [GET /:id]
+ Parameter
    + id: string - Id of user

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    {
        _id: string - Id of user
        createdAt: timestamp - Date of creation of user
        name: string - Name of user
        email: string - Email of user
        password: string - Password of user
        role: string - Role of user
    }

